  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【Story】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a world where humans and the conscious beings known as Kururu coexist. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The study of the essence and mechanisms of Kururu has not yet reached any conclusions that have achieved widespread consensus. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, it is generally agreed that it is a form of life that exists in harmony and resonance with all human mental and physiological rhythms, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >capable of interacting with humans during cognition, thought, or communication. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Humans must maintain a benign balance with Kururu to ensure the stability of their sanity and cognitive abilities. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >However, only a very few humans can visually identify, physically perceive, and manipulate Kururu, and conduct systematic research on them. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We call these individuals \"Tuners.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This summer, Mioi (barely) passed the professional exam and came to Baixiang City as an apprentice Tuner, along with Kasula and Syss.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This is a coastal city with nearly two centuries of history but not much communication with the outside world, which, however, has attracted the attention of the Tuners Association in the past decade. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >As the routine tasks were carried out, this metropolis began to exhibit abnormalities, with phenomena of group dysregulation becoming increasingly common and severe. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >At the same time, two mysterious Tuners who had received special commissions also arrived in Baixiang City... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/2688720d4d873c29bf3763e8d59dac37.avif?t=1737785280\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras_big/2688720d4d873c29bf3763e8d59dac37.avif?t=1737785280 width=800 height=1132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【Exploration】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>· Unravel the Secrets of Baixiang City</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Gain unique encounters through random routes, with each successful patrol bringing you closer to the \"truth.\"</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/8f973efad1e8b226f7f953ae91591d73.poster.avif?t=1737785280\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/8f973efad1e8b226f7f953ae91591d73.webm?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/8f973efad1e8b226f7f953ae91591d73.mp4?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/10371a891b400ac304af3290db13f951.poster.avif?t=1737785280\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/10371a891b400ac304af3290db13f951.webm?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/10371a891b400ac304af3290db13f951.mp4?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>· Card-based City Patrol</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Flip through the perilous mission cards, respond carefully, and make the best adventurous decisions for your team.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/2567f9b36074d6878c6c72696d74e753.avif?t=1737785280\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras_big/2567f9b36074d6878c6c72696d74e753.avif?t=1737785280 width=800 height=1132 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>【Combat】</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>· Magical Girls Forging Ahead</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  Execute splendid combos with a single click, block at the right moment, and engage in fast-paced combat that's simple in attack and defense but infinitely variable!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d3ee0e5e697d91810d35718411aa1428.poster.avif?t=1737785280\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d3ee0e5e697d91810d35718411aa1428.webm?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/d3ee0e5e697d91810d35718411aa1428.mp4?t=1737785280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras/1779676335189067436b05dec657e216.avif?t=1737785280\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1833680/extras_big/1779676335189067436b05dec657e216.avif?t=1737785280 width=800 height=1132 /></span></p>",
